&lt;p>&lt;strong>Large Language Models (LLMs) like GPT-4 don’t actually ‘know’ anything, they predict words based on old training data. Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) changes that by letting AI pull in fresh, real-world knowledge before answering.&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>